snippet.title: "The Judge EXPOSED Me" Amber Heard Official Apology
snippet.description:

“The judge exposed me”. Amber Heard has officially apologized for everything because what I’m about to show you is going to blow you away. The judge seemed to be absolutely done with Amber Heard and her lawyer and we got the whole transcript over here. I don’t think anything else could have happened that would show more clearly than this that Amber Heard is lying, at least. I’m not just saying that; once you hear what the judge had to say to Amber Heard, you’ll actually be surprised.
